    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Because how can you possibly measure your impact? What metric accounts for ‘better than all others?’",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "How about",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "merely better",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "instead.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Better than the guys downtown. Better than what’s on display. Better than your friends.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "You don’t have to be best in all categories to stand out.",
